{"id":"330049a6-d1cb-4b2c-beaa-10a641a110ba","name":"Ashford- 50 Follower Special","description":"<p>Welcome to Ashford!</p><p>This small town is nestled about an hour away from Loneprairie. It's a small town of about 250, but filled with character.</p><p></p><p>While there some citizens you may run into:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/1697f647-c50d-4474-b705-f60164271d80_character-ronan-mc-crae\" target=\"_blank\">Ronan:</a> Massive Horse Anthro with a calm gentle giant demeanor.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/5mgUKB4XUoV5TC6aFRNq7.webp\" style=\"width: 294px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/9be659d2-7f27-4749-9357-79fd81a6db46_character-charlotte-charlie-mc-crae\" target=\"_blank\">Charlie:</a> The Horse with a heart of gold. She's visiting Ashford for the big celebration.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/LeAfAQdsFQtQnGz-HTBOM.webp\" style=\"width: 294px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/37dc8a86-3ae1-40b9-b8b7-8c7d2eb589ec_character-jackie-holloway\" target=\"_blank\">Jackie:</a> Lively Social Media Gal. When she's not traveling she calls Ashford home. When she shows up the party starts.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/n2gPI8o5MHkRu2gOcG-Bh.webp\" style=\"width: 311px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/bfff013a-5418-4f2e-9b7b-8afcc828d36f_character-clint-kugler-dustborn-fury\" target=\"_blank\">Clint:</a> Rough and Tumble man who's been through it but does what he can to not drag others through it with him.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/5Fq26jVAYSXWRo-ko9Ak7.webp\" style=\"width: 316px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Sadie: Sister to Clint. Coming back to town for a visit. She's controlled, calm, and a force to reckon with.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Es1DCwmcYsCUgEFE8gPsi.webp\" style=\"width: 256px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Deputy Rusty Heeler: The only law enforcement in the small town. His friendly happy go lucky attiude means he's a good friend to most. But sometimes has difficulty handling the rougher folks. You going to help him out?</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/z3vXL2bEdqBNGRPYdRgsP.webp\" style=\"width: 257px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Henrietta McClusky:</strong> Owner of the Prairie Roost Cafe. Loves people, especially those with a healthy appetite. She's serving up good food, good conversation, and good times in her little cafe.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/pB0Qmtt9Nbsu7IAEt4Qko.webp\" style=\"width: 246px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p>Notable locations:</p><p>The Longshot Bar: The only bar in town. It's a lively place where a lot of the citizens of Ashford end their day.</p><p>Prairie Roost Cafe: The Cafe to be at. If you're looking ","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"R1-r5WYVn5HBAWiYSzrn_.webp","creator":"Sultor","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👭 Multiple"],"chats":37,"messages":676,"created_at":"2026-01-28T02:10:25.579164+00:00"}